Class PtuPrognosisRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • energy.usef.core.repository.BaseRepository<PtuPrognosis>
      • energy.usef.core.repository.PtuPrognosisRepository

  • public class PtuPrognosisRepository
extends BaseRepository<PtuPrognosis>
    Repository class for the PtuPrognosis entity. This class is in charge of database operations on the tables related to the prognosises.

      • findPrognosesForSettlement

        public List<PtuPrognosis> findPrognosesForSettlement(org.joda.time.LocalDate startDate,
                                                     org.joda.time.LocalDate endDate)
        Find all the Prognosis information needed for initiating the settlement. Prognoses with a period within the interval defined by the variables and with status DocumentStatus.ACCEPTED, DocumentStatus.FINAL and DocumentStatus.ARCHIVED will be retrieved.
        Parameters:
        startDate - LocalDate start date of the settlement (inclusive).
        endDate - LocalDate end date of the settlement (inclusive).
        Returns:
        a List of PtuPrognosis ordered by period, participant domain and ptu index.
